---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import pushImg   from "../assets/renders/mechanism/2.jpg";
import rotateImg from "../assets/renders/mechanism/4.jpg";
import openImg   from "../assets/renders/mechanism/5.jpg";
import lockedImg from "../assets/renders/mechanism/1.jpg";

/**
 * Triple-Action wheel for the BrazLatch mechanism.
 *
 *   FORWARD (human opens):   PUSH → ROTATE → OPEN
 *   REVERSE (human closes):  OPEN → ROTATE → PUSH (→ locked)
 *   INTERRUPTED (animal):    PUSH → RESET   (spring snaps it home; gate never crosses ROTATE)
 *
 * Three latch-image cards arranged on a circle. Bidirectional arrows wrap the
 * perimeter. A center medallion shows the RESET behaviour — the moment that
 * defeats every non-human attempt.
 */
---

<section class="section section-dark border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="container-page">
    <header class="max-w-2xl reveal">
      <p class="kicker">The triple action</p>
      <h2 class="h2-section mt-3">Three motions. One of them is a gate.</h2>
      <p class="lede mt-6">
        Every opening &mdash; and every closing &mdash; runs the same three actions:
        <span class="text-brand-green font-semibold">PUSH</span>,
        <span class="text-brand-green font-semibold">ROTATE</span>,
        <span class="text-brand-green font-semibold">OPEN</span>. Skip the middle one and the spring drives the bolt straight home.
      </p>
    </header>

    <figure class="reveal mx-auto mt-14 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="relative aspect-square w-full bg-brand-ink-deep rounded-sm border border-brand-bone/10 p-3 sm:p-5">
        <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 w-3 h-3 border-l border-t border-brand-green/50" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="absolute top-2 right-2 w-3 h-3 border-r border-t border-brand-green/50" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="absolute bottom-2 left-2 w-3 h-3 border-l border-b border-brand-green/50" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-3 h-3 border-r border-b border-brand-green/50" aria-hidden="true"></span>

        <!-- Arrow layer (full-bleed) -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 720 720" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
          <defs>
            <marker id="tw-arrow-green" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#009444"/>
            </marker>
            <marker id="tw-arrow-amber" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#C46A2E"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>

          <!-- Faint guide ring -->
          <circle cx="360" cy="360" r="248" fill="none" stroke="#EFEAE0" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.05" stroke-dasharray="2 5"/>

          <!--
            Card centers on a 248-radius circle:
              PUSH    (top, 90°):     (360, 112)
              ROTATE  (lower-right):  (575, 484)   [angle -30° / 330°]
              OPEN    (lower-left):   (145, 484)   [angle 210°]
            Arrows are arcs of radius 248 with both ends shortened so arrowheads
            sit clear of the cards (card half-diagonal ≈ 110px).
          -->

          <!-- PUSH → ROTATE -->
          <path d="M 458 158 A 248 248 0 0 1 575 372"
                fill="none" stroke="#009444" stroke-width="2.5"
                marker-start="url(#tw-arrow-green)" marker-end="url(#tw-arrow-green)"/>
          <!-- ROTATE → OPEN -->
          <path d="M 519 552 A 248 248 0 0 1 201 552"
                fill="none" stroke="#009444" stroke-width="2.5"
                marker-start="url(#tw-arrow-green)" marker-end="url(#tw-arrow-green)"/>
          <!-- OPEN → PUSH (closes the wheel) -->
          <path d="M 145 372 A 248 248 0 0 1 262 158"
                fill="none" stroke="#009444" stroke-width="2.5"
                marker-start="url(#tw-arrow-green)" marker-end="url(#tw-arrow-green)"/>

          <!-- Reset loop: tiny circular arrow next to PUSH card showing it bounces back to itself -->
          <g transform="translate(360, 290)">
            <path d="M -34 0 A 34 34 0 1 1 34 0"
                  fill="none" stroke="#C46A2E" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="5 4"
                  marker-end="url(#tw-arrow-amber)"/>
          </g>
        </svg>

        <!-- PUSH card -->
        <div class="absolute z-10 w-[30%]" style="top: 4%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);">
          <div class="relative rounded-sm bg-brand-ink-deep border border-brand-green/60 shadow-card-green overflow-hidden">
            <div class="relative aspect-square bg-brand-ink">
              <Image src={pushImg} alt="Latch in pushed state — pin advancing along the channel" widths={[240, 360]} sizes="30vw" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90"/>
              <span class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 border-l border-t border-brand-green/60"></span>
              <span class="absolute top-1 right-1 w-2 h-2 border-r border-t border-brand-green/60"></span>
              <span class="absolute bottom-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 border-l border-b border-brand-green/60"></span>
              <span class="absolute bottom-1 right-1 w-2 h-2 border-r border-b border-brand-green/60"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="px-3 py-2.5 text-center">
              <p class="font-mono text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] text-brand-green tracking-[0.2em]">ACTION 01</p>
              <p class="mt-0.5 font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-bone tracking-wide">PUSH</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ROTATE card (lower-right) -->
        <div class="absolute z-10 w-[30%]" style="bottom: 7%; right: 4%;">
          <div class="relative rounded-sm bg-brand-ink-deep border border-brand-green shadow-card-green overflow-hidden ring-2 ring-brand-green/40 ring-offset-2 ring-offset-brand-ink-deep">
            <div class="relative aspect-square bg-brand-ink">
              <Image src={rotateImg} alt="Latch being rotated — pin lifts out of the channel" widths={[240, 360]} sizes="30vw" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"/>
              <span class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 border-l border-t border-brand-green/80"></span>
              <span class="absolute top-1 right-1 w-2 h-2 border-r border-t border-brand-green/80"></span>
              <span class="absolute bottom-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 border-l border-b border-brand-green/80"></span>
              <span class="absolute bottom-1 right-1 w-2 h-2 border-r border-b border-brand-green/80"></span>
              <span class="absolute top-1.5 right-1.5 font-mono text-[9px] text-brand-bone bg-brand-green/90 px-1.5 py-0.5 tracking-wider">GATE</span>
            </div>
            <div class="px-3 py-2.5 text-center">
              <p class="font-mono text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] text-brand-green tracking-[0.2em]">ACTION 02</p>
              <p class="mt-0.5 font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-bone tracking-wide">ROTATE</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- OPEN / CLOSE card (lower-left) -->
        <div class="absolute z-10 w-[30%]" style="bottom: 7%; left: 4%;">
          <div class="relative rounded-sm bg-brand-ink-deep border border-brand-green/60 shadow-card-green overflow-hidden">
            <div class="relative aspect-square bg-brand-ink">
              <Image src={openImg} alt="Latch open — bolt retracted, gate releases" widths={[240, 360]} sizes="30vw" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90"/>
              <span class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 border-l border-t border-brand-green/60"></span>
              <span class="absolute top-1 right-1 w-2 h-2 border-r border-t border-brand-green/60"></span>
              <span class="absolute bottom-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 border-l border-b border-brand-green/60"></span>
              <span class="absolute bottom-1 right-1 w-2 h-2 border-r border-b border-brand-green/60"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="px-3 py-2.5 text-center">
              <p class="font-mono text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] text-brand-green tracking-[0.2em]">ACTION 03</p>
              <p class="mt-0.5 font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-bone tracking-wide">OPEN <span class="text-brand-bone-muted font-normal text-xs sm:text-sm">/ CLOSE</span></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Central RESET medallion -->
        <div class="absolute z-10 left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[26%]">
          <div class="rounded-full border border-brand-amber/60 bg-brand-ink-deep/95 aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-3 shadow-card-amber">
            <p class="font-mono text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] text-brand-amber tracking-[0.22em]">NO ROTATION</p>
            <p class="mt-1 font-display text-sm sm:text-base font-bold text-brand-bone tracking-wide">RESET</p>
            <p class="mt-1.5 text-[10px] sm:text-[11px] text-brand-bone-muted leading-tight">spring drives bolt<br/>back to locked</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <figcaption class="mt-10 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-green/30 bg-brand-green/[0.05] p-5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="inline-block w-6 h-[2px] bg-brand-green" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-brand-green">Human hand</p>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-[12px] text-brand-bone/80">open  · PUSH → ROTATE → OPEN<br/>close · PUSH → ROTATE → CLOSE</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-brand-bone/90 leading-relaxed">
            Three actions, one motion. The L-handle is the only thing that can hold the push while delivering the rotation. Without that grip, action 02 never happens.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-amber/30 bg-brand-amber/[0.05] p-5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="inline-block w-6 h-[2px]" style="background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,#C46A2E 0 4px,transparent 4px 7px);" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-brand-amber">Animal · accident · vibration</p>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-[12px] text-brand-bone/80">reset · PUSH → RESET</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-brand-bone/90 leading-relaxed">
            A nose, a paw, a leaned shoulder, a bumped object &mdash; anything that can push but can't switch grip to twist. The pin gets as far as the gate, finds no rotation, and the spring sends it home. Every time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>
